{"tid":1412371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(認同請推、討論)下一步：罷買？","createTime":"2019-08-05T06:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:51:47.000Z","uid":258267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67f9e420c2e8fd318e395a221800741ac23f1b83","tid":1412371,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"各位係現場集會既巴絲，多謝大家願意為香港罷一日工。<br />\n但係罷工始終唔係咁易長期作戰，罷買不但可以長久，而且可以對準紅企，顯示經濟影響力，會唔會真係試下執行？<br />\n方案可以係逢一、三、五罷食/買一個紅色企業，而且仲吹雞去唔同區快閃叫口號抗議，咁先會見到個效果。<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n星期日講定星期一八點：<br />\n大家樂-北角xx，黃大仙xx，天水圍xx。<br />\n認同請推同熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c60c866aa36627e0f114b401fc7c4290cf611","tid":1412371,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"efe43323ccd9b3c0ea548476053b40d9ac700784","tid":1412371,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"c4be8851e7f1e09e5f5e59e9d7e9c4db0e6f404c","tid":1412371,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你叫罷買，就會分到邊間係黃，就會勝利球迷大量入場</span>"},{"pid":"8906c8c561cb81631044d7f171c53141efa73c82","tid":1412371,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"[repost]香港點算？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7cf4b4d2c77a6dc036009eed1936ca5370b4348","tid":1412371,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4be8851e7f1e09e5f5e59e9d7e9c4db0e6f404c","tid":1412371,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"reply